            <ab>To Arrios Herakleides, strategos of the division of Herakleides (of the Arsinoite nome) from Aphrodisios (son of ...) weaver, from (the village of ...). In the evening (of the x day) of the current month (...) a certain Petheus and (... and) others joining (those from?) the village approached (...) and having no (...) they snatched away ...</ab>
